data.description: This charming house, move-in ready and waiting for you, features 3 cozy bedrooms and 1.5 well-appointed bathrooms. An attached 1-car garage and a large backyard offer ample space for both convenience and leisure. Enjoy the California sunshine on the covered patio, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Inside, the kitchen shines with stainless steel appliances, making meal prep a breeze. The guest bathroom, complete with a shower/tub combo, ensures comfort and convenience for your guests. Freshly updated exterior paint and an attractive overall appearance make this house not just a home, but a retreat. Situated near the Lemoore Naval Air Station and Lemoore High School, you're in a vibrant community with easy access to local amenities. Don't miss out on making this adorable and practical house your own!
